Usage: alias [-help] <new_cmd> [<old_cmd>] [-args {{<new> <old>} ...}]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<new_cmd>                     # A new alias command name. It can be the same as
                              # <old_name> if you only want to add -args
                              # aliases. (string, required)
<old_cmd>                     # An existing command name. (string, optional)
-args {{<new> <old>} ...}     # A list of old arg and new alias arg names.
                              # (string, optional)